    {
        "source_sentence": "「善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220b_304:0550c16_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於甚深般若波羅蜜多中，苦聖諦無所有，集、滅、道聖諦無所有。",
