        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220b_304:0551b06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於甚深般若波羅蜜多中，一切陀羅尼門無所有，一切三摩地門無所有。",
